===Noun===
'''fertilizer''' ([[uncountable]] and [[countable]]; plural: [[fertilizers]])

# A [[natural]] [[substance]] that is used to make the [[ground]] more suitable for [[grow]]ing [[plant]]s.
# A [[chemical]] [[compound]] created to have the same effect.

